oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Unidentified girl with ribbon in her hair
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The young girl in this image had long, dark hair, held back by a ribbon, tied in a bow atop her head. Her dark dress had a fan front bodice and a white-trimmed high neck.; This image of an unidentified girl is from an old photograph album found at an estate sale.
